INSERT INTO infos_category_english VALUES('1','About Us','','<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Company Background</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Homlan International was established in 1987, and has been persist in excellent corporate image throughout computer industry for decades. By produce and distribute innovative, up to date monitors for both domestic and international customers, we have managed to become one of the best displays supplier in the industry.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The company&rsquo;s view is to be sustainable operational. The objective includes develop new displays for relative goods and improve the products&rsquo; performance, value and service quality. This philosophy has admittedly led the company to a steady growth.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>For 27 years, Homlan has constructed out sound provinces-through marketing channels and professional maintenance logistics systems.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In 1995, Homlan established &ldquo;Displays Orphanage&rdquo;, to help dealers and consumers who are troubled by missing sellers and could find nowhere for repair services.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Homlan has always believed in &ldquo;specialized display, quality first and leading services&rdquo;. Finally, under great expectation, the self owned brand &lsquo;Viewtec&rsquo; was established. During the global economic downturn, Viewtec uphold the unvarying principle and continue thriving to give Taiwan information industry the best display supplies.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Homlan has always being understanding the markets&rsquo; need with an open mind and our view towards the future. Only with these can we sustainingly keep up with the market trend and provide our customers&rsquo; real and best solutions.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Since 1995 Homlan established &ldquo;Displays Orphanage&rdquo;, giving dealers and consumers who have &ldquo;displays orphan&rdquo; a comfortable, safe and guaranteed home.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In order to progress steadily and be down-to-earth while keep on growing, we need helpful comrades who not only pursuit of profit but also understand the idea of sustainable operation. As a team, we together help our customers select quality displays, avoid letting customers get lost within the turbulence of brand. We continue to innovate, improve our products&rsquo; quality and functions, as well as customer services with unremitting effort, and have gained most favorable comments.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Besides providing a satisfactory variety of displays and related goods, Homlan is also positive of introducing more kinds of product to meet the fast changing market. We focus on various professional fields, for example touch and tablet monitors, LCD monitors, LCD TV, digital signage, CCTV/surveillance use monitor, bus exclusive monitor, dental use monitor, open frame and industrial use monitor, etc. And what&rsquo;s more, we provide various brands&rsquo; display recycle and services.</div>','2','1','1','0','','1','250','','0','2','2012-06-07 15:22:59','60.250.156.136','5','2013-12-24 17:02:25','59.115.52.33','0','1','','','0','編號','標題','簡單說明','優惠價','操作','1','1','1','1','1','0');
